Class ScatterIntervalsByNs

java.lang.Object

      picard.util.ScatterIntervalsByNs

public class ScatterIntervalsByNs
extends CommandLineProgram

A CLP for breaking up a reference into intervals of Ns and ACGTs bases. Used for creating a broken-up interval list for calling WGS.

Author:
Yossi Farjoun
